update Jennifer (neutral)
Jennifer: Ako lang ang nagpaniwalang kaya niyang kalimutan.
The memories begin to shatter like broken glass.
The laughter fades.
The colors distort.
The familiar electronic buzzing returns.
The flashback begins collapsing around Jennifer.
The screen flickers violently.
Preparing to pull her back to the present...
